com.androidanimator.animation

Interface Combinable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FadeInAnimation, FadeOutAnimation, FlipHorizontalAnimation, FlipVerticalAnimation, PathAnimation, RotationAnimation, ScaleInAnimation, ScaleOutAnimation, SlideInAnimation, SlideOutAnimation

    public interface Combinable
    This interface is implemented only by animation classes that can be combined to animate together.
